00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:47.580
♫ The sky that seems so far away ♫

00:00:47.580 --> 00:00:53.160
♫ And the sea that seems so vast ♫

00:00:53.160 --> 00:00:55.080
♫ I just watch the waves all day ♫

00:00:55.080 --> 00:00:56.960
♫ Knowing we can never meet ♫

00:00:56.960 --> 00:01:02.750
♫ Our hearts that beat as one ♫

00:01:02.750 --> 00:01:08.030
♫ But the world will never listen ♫

