♫ Though the rules of this world
Forbid us from being one ♫

00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:27.660
♫ This love is about you and me
And no one else ♫

00:01:27.660 --> 00:01:31.380
♫ We don't have to tell the world
we're in love ♫

00:01:31.380 --> 00:01:36.080
♫ We don't have to tell anyone
and make it messy ♫

00:01:36.080 --> 00:01:38.460
♫ Let you be my world ♫

00:01:38.460 --> 00:01:42.640
♫ Let's live in our own new world together ♫

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:46.330
♫ We don't have to tell the world
we're together ♫

00:01:46.330 --> 00:01:51.060
♫ Because none of that matters at all ♫

00:01:51.060 --> 00:01:53.170
♫ As long as our hearts are one ♫

00:01:53.170 --> 00:01:55.060
♫ As long as you are with me ♫

00:01:55.060 --> 00:01:57.400
♫ As long as we love each other ♫

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:00.336
♫ We don't have to tell anyone ♫

00:02:00.336 --> 00:02:05.550
[Lover Merman — Only Nava]
♫ We don't have to tell anyone ♫

00:02:05.550 --> 00:02:07.740
[Previously]
Will you be my boyfriend?

00:02:07.740 --> 00:02:09.760
Okay. Let's date.

00:02:09.760 --> 00:02:13.520
If anything like that happens again, you have to tell me immediately.

00:02:13.520 --> 00:02:16.980
I understand how you feel.

00:02:16.980 --> 00:02:20.520
If something bad ever happened
to my own dear brother,

00:02:20.520 --> 00:02:22.430
I'd feel the same way.

00:02:22.430 --> 00:02:23.870
We grew up together, Than.

00:02:23.870 --> 00:02:26.910
Do you really think Dad
would accept it if he found out?

00:02:26.910 --> 00:02:30.590
Because what I'm going to do is keep on loving you.

00:02:30.590 --> 00:02:32.390
Because I don't know

00:02:32.390 --> 00:02:35.490
if I could ever love anyone else if it's not you.

00:02:35.490 --> 00:02:39.541
I know you've been investigating
the concession rights and the mermaid hunters.

00:02:39.541 --> 00:02:40.980
Drop it.

00:02:40.980 --> 00:02:42.210
Why?

00:02:42.210 --> 00:02:44.900
I will handle this myself.

00:02:44.900 --> 00:02:47.470
You getting involved when you don't fully
understand the situation

00:02:47.470 --> 00:02:49.310
will only cause problems for me.

00:02:49.310 --> 00:02:50.870
It's just that since I moved here,

00:02:50.870 --> 00:02:53.300
I've never seen Nava work
on a full moon day. Not once.

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:56.560
I just saw another merperson swimming that way.

00:02:56.560 --> 00:03:00.910
Should we go take a look? I want to know who it is.

00:03:00.910 --> 00:03:03.950
If we hadn't met in the water,
we never would have known.

00:03:05.030 --> 00:03:08.220
I had a feeling the first time I met you, Ping,

00:03:08.220 --> 00:03:10.420
I'm half-human.

00:03:10.420 --> 00:03:13.040
My parents fell in love...

00:03:13.040 --> 00:03:15.380
My mom didn't know my dad was a merman.

00:03:16.620 --> 00:03:18.470
Are you staying here tonight?

00:03:18.470 --> 00:03:20.900
I'm just keeping my promise.

00:03:42.200 --> 00:03:44.540
[Phraphai]

00:06:48.740 --> 00:06:50.740
It's not just a near miss.

00:06:50.740 --> 00:06:53.350
I think I'm on a direct collision course
with you.

00:07:30.270 --> 00:07:34.100
We've had a lot more customers this past month.

00:07:34.100 --> 00:07:37.040
I think we should increase our alcohol stock.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:39.080
We're running out fast.

00:07:39.080 --> 00:07:40.180
Yeah, sure.

00:07:40.180 --> 00:07:43.280
I'll talk to the mainland supplier myself.

00:07:44.430 --> 00:07:46.840
What do you think about food supplies?

00:07:47.680 --> 00:07:49.000
We should increase those, too.

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:51.190
But check the ingredient prices carefully,

00:07:51.190 --> 00:07:54.560
or we'll end up taking a loss.

00:07:54.560 --> 00:07:57.910
Yeah, I'll take care of that at the market.

00:07:57.910 --> 00:08:00.160
Let's stick to the plan then.

00:08:00.160 --> 00:08:02.460
Okay, I'll get going.

00:08:02.460 --> 00:08:03.960
Yeah.

00:08:17.390 --> 00:08:20.850
Do you want some orange cake? Aunt Son said it's your favorite.

00:08:20.850 --> 00:08:22.480
No, thanks.

00:08:25.640 --> 00:08:28.090
I heard you're going to restock the bar today.

00:08:28.090 --> 00:08:30.090
Want me to come help?

00:08:31.140 --> 00:08:34.020
That's okay. I can handle it.

00:08:37.490 --> 00:08:39.770
Are you okay, Phana?

00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:42.160
What do you mean?

00:08:42.160 --> 00:08:43.990
It's just... the past few days,

00:08:43.990 --> 00:08:46.920
you don't seem like you want to talk to me.

00:08:46.920 --> 00:08:50.130
Did I do something to upset you?

00:08:52.330 --> 00:08:53.830
Ping,

00:08:55.150 --> 00:08:58.010
I think we should keep
some distance for a while.

00:08:58.010 --> 00:09:00.680
I feel like we've gotten too close.

00:09:00.680 --> 00:09:02.850
I'm worried about what people might think.

00:09:03.780 --> 00:09:05.820
Who would think badly of us?

00:09:05.820 --> 00:09:09.720
You and Nava are close too, right? Like siblings.

00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:12.490
Nava and I grew up together.

00:09:12.490 --> 00:09:14.300
But you...

00:09:14.300 --> 00:09:17.930
you're my employee, and I'm your boss.

00:09:20.110 --> 00:09:21.700
I don't understand.

00:09:21.700 --> 00:09:24.800
Bosses and employees aren't usually this close.

00:09:24.800 --> 00:09:26.980
I don't treat anyone else specially,

00:09:26.980 --> 00:09:29.650
so why should I make an exception for you?

00:09:30.540 --> 00:09:35.000
So you did think I was special?

00:09:35.000 --> 00:09:38.557
No. I never thought that.

00:09:38.557 --> 00:09:43.227
The reason we got so close was because I had just broken up with Namhom.

00:09:43.227 --> 00:09:45.527
I was lonely. That's all.

00:09:47.897 --> 00:09:50.477
Then let me ask you directly.

00:09:51.427 --> 00:09:53.877
How do you feel about me, Phana?

00:09:55.347 --> 00:09:57.847
I don't know.

00:09:57.847 --> 00:10:00.087
How do you feel about me?

00:10:01.067 --> 00:10:05.897
For me you're more than just my boss.

00:10:09.137 --> 00:10:14.387
But I'm sorry for crossing the line.

00:11:02.677 --> 00:11:05.117
Hey, what's wrong with you, Phana?

00:11:05.117 --> 00:11:06.977
Nothing.

00:11:06.977 --> 00:11:09.027
I'm just spacing out.

00:11:11.317 --> 00:11:14.397
This is about Ping, isn't it?

00:11:19.127 --> 00:11:23.577
I talked to him about us keeping our distance.

00:11:25.357 --> 00:11:31.277
But I don't know if I did the right thing by telling him that.

00:11:32.097 --> 00:11:36.337
Didn't you tell me you wanted to figure out your own feelings first?

00:11:37.177 --> 00:11:39.127
Yeah.

00:11:39.127 --> 00:11:43.377
But I still don't know how I feel.

00:11:44.397 --> 00:11:49.457
All I know is... Ping has already developed feelings.

00:11:51.617 --> 00:11:56.307
And I know I ended up hurting him.

00:11:58.537 --> 00:12:01.307
But the worst part is,

00:12:01.307 --> 00:12:05.627
I don't even know how I really feel about him.

00:12:06.937 --> 00:12:13.317
Or if maybe, like you said, I was just using him to replace Namhom.

00:12:15.207 --> 00:12:20.277
Maybe I don't really want Ping after all.

00:12:31.457 --> 00:12:34.327
It's not wrong for you
to feel that way right now.

00:12:35.247 --> 00:12:39.967
But I think you should give yourself a little more time.

00:12:39.967 --> 00:12:45.047
Once you're sure about your feelings, then you can decide what to do.

00:12:47.577 --> 00:12:49.877
Yeah, you're probably right.

00:12:49.877 --> 00:12:52.547
I really haven't figured it out yet.

00:13:00.607 --> 00:13:03.017
Phurich, I'm running a fever all of a sudden.

00:13:03.017 --> 00:13:05.037
I have to go home early.

00:13:05.037 --> 00:13:06.837
Is something wrong?

00:13:42.237 --> 00:13:44.337
I'm home, Mom.

00:13:49.687 --> 00:13:52.377
I brought you some desserts.

00:13:55.437 --> 00:13:58.727
I'll leave them in the kitchen, okay?

00:14:09.337 --> 00:14:13.027
Aren't you supposed to be at your internship?
Why are you back?

00:14:29.877 --> 00:14:31.997
Don't tell me... they found out, did they?

00:14:31.997 --> 00:14:34.317
That you're a monster.

00:14:47.647 --> 00:14:50.127
If everyone finds out what you really are,

00:14:50.127 --> 00:14:52.717
what am I supposed to tell them?
That my son's a freak?

00:14:52.717 --> 00:14:54.997
But Ping is our child.

00:14:54.997 --> 00:14:58.407
If I had a choice,
I wouldn't want a child like this!

00:15:08.357 --> 00:15:12.167
Phana, I need to take one more sick day.

00:15:12.167 --> 00:15:14.607
I already texted Phurich,

00:15:14.607 --> 00:15:16.307
but he's on the mainland,

00:15:16.307 --> 00:15:19.897
so he told me to let you know myself.

00:15:19.897 --> 00:15:22.077
Have you taken any medicine?

00:15:27.757 --> 00:15:29.547
Phana, are you okay?

00:15:29.547 --> 00:15:31.817
You look stressed.

00:15:31.817 --> 00:15:37.157
Oh, Ping just texted.
He's taking another sick day.

00:15:37.157 --> 00:15:40.477
Is everything okay between you and Ping?

00:15:41.317 --> 00:15:43.707
Why? Did you hear something?

00:15:43.707 --> 00:15:46.467
I can tell just by looking at your face.

00:15:49.637 --> 00:15:54.137
It's nothing serious.

00:15:54.137 --> 00:15:58.217
I'm just not really sure
about my own feelings.

00:15:59.517 --> 00:16:04.827
I don't know what's going on between you and Ping right now,

00:16:05.887 --> 00:16:09.987
but I don't want to see you looking all sad and lonely like this.

00:16:12.917 --> 00:16:15.707
If there's anything I can do to help,

00:16:15.707 --> 00:16:17.607
please let me know.

00:16:18.647 --> 00:16:20.347
Thanks.

00:16:25.737 --> 00:16:27.367
Hello, Phana.

00:16:27.367 --> 00:16:29.237
Oh, Phraphai.

00:16:29.237 --> 00:16:32.147
What brings you all the way
out to the bar today?

00:16:32.147 --> 00:16:35.677
I have something I need to discuss
with you and Nava.

00:16:37.567 --> 00:16:39.687
You sound serious.

00:16:39.687 --> 00:16:41.387
A little, yes.

00:16:41.387 --> 00:16:43.287
Alright, I'll get straight to the point.

00:16:43.287 --> 00:16:46.687
You've heard about
the merman sea concession, right?

00:16:46.687 --> 00:16:48.777
Yeah, I've heard a little about it.

00:16:48.777 --> 00:16:52.077
Humans have started hunting merfolk
on the island.

00:16:52.077 --> 00:16:54.297
Several have been kidnapped...

00:16:54.297 --> 00:16:56.767
some have even been killed.

00:16:56.767 --> 00:16:59.197
My father and I are investigating it,

00:16:59.197 --> 00:17:01.787
and we suspect it might be connected

00:17:01.787 --> 00:17:05.107
to humans encroaching on merman territory.

00:17:05.107 --> 00:17:07.117
So you're saying...

00:17:07.117 --> 00:17:10.507
what happened 20 years ago could be happening all over again?

00:17:10.507 --> 00:17:11.597
Possibly.

00:17:11.597 --> 00:17:13.847
I can't say for sure yet.

00:17:13.847 --> 00:17:16.557
We don't have enough evidence.

00:17:16.557 --> 00:17:21.077
But this situation has already made all the merfolk on the island terrified.

00:17:21.077 --> 00:17:24.990
When this happens, I don't feel safe at all.

00:17:25.770 --> 00:17:27.930
Especially for Nava.

00:17:29.760 --> 00:17:32.670
Phana, that's why I came to talk to you.

00:17:32.670 --> 00:17:37.250
From now on, I'll be personally responsible for Nava's safety.

00:17:39.830 --> 00:17:42.570
My safety? What do you mean, Phraphai?

00:17:43.810 --> 00:17:47.990
Nava, from now on, I'll take you to and from work.

00:17:47.990 --> 00:17:51.690
If you need to go anywhere, you tell me.

00:17:51.690 --> 00:17:55.740
And at night, I'll have Met watch over you.

00:17:58.090 --> 00:18:03.680
Why does it sound like you're putting me on probation?

00:18:03.680 --> 00:18:06.840
Nava, please understand.

00:18:06.840 --> 00:18:11.960
I'm only doing this for your safety.

00:18:12.890 --> 00:18:14.460
Don't forget,

00:18:14.460 --> 00:18:20.200
the one who suffered the most
from what happened 20 years ago was you.

00:18:20.200 --> 00:18:23.630
I don't want anything bad
to happen to you again.

00:18:24.600 --> 00:18:25.810
But...

00:18:25.810 --> 00:18:29.690
I think you should do as Phraphai says.

00:18:29.690 --> 00:18:32.700
I don't want to see you get hurt again.

00:18:36.870 --> 00:18:39.550
Please take good care of him, Phraphai.

00:18:39.550 --> 00:18:41.260
Of course.

00:18:41.260 --> 00:18:44.990
In that case, I'll come by tonight
to pick you up.

00:18:46.060 --> 00:18:47.760
Nava,

00:18:48.610 --> 00:18:51.340
I'm really worried about you.

00:18:51.340 --> 00:18:53.340
I'll be going now.

00:18:54.590 --> 00:18:56.780
I'll be going then, Phana.

00:19:14.700 --> 00:19:16.290
Nava,

00:19:16.290 --> 00:19:21.040
I want to ask you something directly about Phurich.

00:19:24.070 --> 00:19:26.033
Please be honest.

00:19:26.033 --> 00:19:30.430
What is your relationship with him right now?

00:19:32.616 --> 00:19:35.316
We're dating.

00:19:36.293 --> 00:19:39.263
I know perfectly well that our kind
shouldn't get involved with humans.

00:19:40.190 --> 00:19:44.360
Especially when it comes to love. It's forbidden.

00:19:46.600 --> 00:19:48.860
But as...

00:19:51.670 --> 00:19:54.860
as a being with a heart, just like them,

00:19:56.010 --> 00:19:58.990
I'm asking to follow my own heart.

00:20:00.850 --> 00:20:02.840
I understand, Nava.

00:20:02.840 --> 00:20:08.000
But I still want you to listen to what Phraphai and I are saying.

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:13.270
At the very least, I want you to do as Phraphai says for now.

00:20:13.270 --> 00:20:17.240
Just until we're sure that you're really safe.

00:20:17.240 --> 00:20:18.840
Okay?

00:20:31.990 --> 00:20:35.840
Nava, let's go home.

00:20:36.580 --> 00:20:38.970
Uh... Phurich.

00:20:38.970 --> 00:20:41.600
- I...
- Nava.

00:20:41.600 --> 00:20:43.880
I'm here to pick you up.

00:20:43.880 --> 00:20:46.450
What does that mean?

00:20:46.450 --> 00:20:47.970
It's a personal matter.

00:20:47.970 --> 00:20:50.450
I don't need to explain myself to you.

00:20:51.530 --> 00:20:54.610
Let's go, Nava. We're going home.

00:20:56.400 --> 00:20:58.510
What's going on, Nava?

00:21:02.260 --> 00:21:04.260
I'm sorry.

00:21:05.940 --> 00:21:08.370
With everything that's happening...

00:21:09.120 --> 00:21:11.890
I just can't explain it to you right now.

00:21:14.700 --> 00:21:16.700
But I promise,

00:21:17.980 --> 00:21:20.220
when things get better,

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:24.500
I'll tell you everything myself.

00:21:42.990 --> 00:21:44.990
You knew about this, didn't you?

00:21:46.590 --> 00:21:48.900
Why are you doing this?

00:21:49.960 --> 00:21:53.080
You have Phraphai picking Nava up
and dropping him off every day,

00:21:53.080 --> 00:21:55.720
and you even have people watching his house.

00:21:55.720 --> 00:21:57.780
What's your game here?

00:21:57.780 --> 00:21:59.610
Trust me, Phu.

00:21:59.610 --> 00:22:02.400
Phraphai and I have our reasons.

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:04.610
What reasons?

00:22:05.220 --> 00:22:07.320
Or are you just trying to keep
Nava and me apart?

00:22:07.320 --> 00:22:08.870
Calm the hell down.

00:22:08.870 --> 00:22:11.040
Then why are you doing this?

00:22:11.840 --> 00:22:13.980
You're acting like Nava's in danger.

00:22:13.980 --> 00:22:16.330
He is.

00:22:16.330 --> 00:22:19.930
Everything we're doing is to protect him.

00:22:21.600 --> 00:22:23.600
What do you mean?

00:22:25.130 --> 00:22:27.360
Who's trying to hurt him?

00:22:30.050 --> 00:22:33.260
Calm down and listen to me, Phu.

00:22:33.260 --> 00:22:37.410
Right now, no one has done anything to Nava.

00:22:38.110 --> 00:22:41.070
But something might happen.

00:22:42.190 --> 00:22:44.200
On this island,

00:22:44.200 --> 00:22:48.890
there are a lot of complicated things going on,

00:22:48.890 --> 00:22:51.930
and I can't explain everything
to you right now.

00:22:54.930 --> 00:22:58.090
All I'm asking you to do right now

00:22:58.090 --> 00:23:00.460
is trust me...

00:23:00.460 --> 00:23:02.360
and trust Nava.

00:23:02.360 --> 00:23:04.480
That's all I ask.

00:23:07.380 --> 00:23:10.040
Then why does it have to be Phraphai?

00:23:10.040 --> 00:23:13.000
Why can't you and I protect him?

00:23:13.670 --> 00:23:16.890
You're like his real brother, aren't you?

00:23:17.550 --> 00:23:19.199
Oh, Phu…

00:23:19.199 --> 00:23:21.779
I don't know how to explain this to you.

00:24:01.980 --> 00:24:03.730
Hello, Phana.

00:24:03.730 --> 00:24:06.110
How are you feeling?

00:24:06.110 --> 00:24:08.210
Still not much better.

00:24:09.430 --> 00:24:10.930
Do you need anything?

00:24:10.930 --> 00:24:13.360
I can have Lek bring it to the resort for you.

00:24:14.520 --> 00:24:17.460
I came home two or three days ago.

00:24:17.460 --> 00:24:19.460
I'm not at the resort.

00:24:21.942 --> 00:24:25.162
You're not trying to avoid me, are you?

00:24:28.290 --> 00:24:31.630
If I said yes...

00:24:31.630 --> 00:24:34.270
that I really am avoiding you...

00:24:34.940 --> 00:24:37.180
what would you do?

00:24:41.830 --> 00:24:45.160
Would you not feel anything at all?

00:24:45.160 --> 00:24:47.160
I...

00:24:49.740 --> 00:24:51.740
I don't know.

00:24:53.110 --> 00:24:57.790
Phana, I'd like to resign.

00:25:03.280 --> 00:25:05.760
I'll take that as your acknowledgement.

00:25:08.470 --> 00:25:10.740
What about your internship, Ping?

00:25:10.740 --> 00:25:13.780
If you don't complete it,
how will you graduate?

00:25:14.980 --> 00:25:18.620
Did you even think about yourself
when you made this decision?

00:25:18.620 --> 00:25:21.010
Why do you care?

00:25:21.010 --> 00:25:24.840
You always just say, "I don't know."

00:25:24.840 --> 00:25:27.990
I'm just an employee to you.

00:25:27.990 --> 00:25:29.450
So please, stop caring.

00:25:29.450 --> 00:25:31.860
Yeah, fine.

00:25:31.860 --> 00:25:34.740
If you think this is best,
then do whatever you want.

00:25:34.740 --> 00:25:36.300
Go wherever you want.

00:25:36.300 --> 00:25:38.520
I don't care anymore.

00:25:40.540 --> 00:25:43.730
Okay. That's all, then.

00:26:24.790 --> 00:26:26.130
It's been a while.

00:26:26.130 --> 00:26:28.680
Oh, Silp! Hello.

